    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Considering TD, I think that refineries and silos should be able to hold a certain volume of tiberium, rather than a certain value. Refineries currently have capacity for one harvester load of green tiberium (value $700), whereas I think they should have capacity for one harvester load, regardless of the tib colour. If the first load is blue tiberium (value $1200) then a silo is required immediately."
